&lt;h1 id="american-spring"&gt;American Spring&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Jan 15 2016&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A one party system ran the United States, and the United States ran the world.&lt;/p&gt;
